@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rmkqcy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v2 + 0.20) - v0))
    v0 = wp.exp((0.16 / (tmp + 0.81 / v2 + 0.75)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.11)))
    data[tid] = v0
